<section class="brand-statement">
  <div class="brand-statement__inner">
    <p class="brand-statement__text reveal">
      The Corner Box exists for the collector who already knows the difference between a
      warehouse find and a curated acquisition. Every issue here has been handled,
      examined, and selected — not aggregated from a database.
    </p>
    <p class="brand-statement__text reveal">
      We drop infrequently. We photograph every copy ourselves. We write notes on
      significance, not just on grade. The price reflects the work.
    </p>
    <p class="brand-statement__text reveal">
      If that sounds like how you prefer to buy — you're in the right place.
    </p>
    <div class="brand-statement__ctas reveal">
      <a class="brand-statement__cta" href="/pages/about">About The Corner Box &rarr;</a>
      <a class="brand-statement__cta" href="/blogs/the-ledger">Browse The Ledger &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

